<br>
However as far as there epics go...there are better droppable weapons for them out there. I still see bard epic used alot because the proc is a good melee buff. Heh don't see too many clerics 60 + w/o epic specially since they made it easier to get. <br>
<br>
As far as sham/druid/necro I don't think any item that gives you a mana free dot is useless. Yeah it doesn't do a whole lot of damage since most of the mobs 60 + have in excess of 35k hp but still damage is damage. <br>
<br>
Now speaking Tank classes. You are absolutely right I have never seen a pally with epic and only one SK with theres. Some warriors use one of there epic swords due to its hate building proc...but with addition of PoP expansion some REALLY nice warrior weapons showed up so you don't really see it much anymore.<br>
<br>
