<br>
Koadic's Endless Intellect, lvl 60 Luclin spell for enchanters.  Upgrades are Tranquility and Voice of Quellious.  Mana regen, + mana, +int/wis.<br>
<br>
 <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>And did shamans/druids ever get Complete heal?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Sort of.  Shaman one is a 1950hp heal for 400 mana, the druid one at 58 is about 3k hp for 400mana.  Forget the hp/mana on the later heal.  <br>
<br>
Enchanters get a better haste spell with PoP.<br>
<br>
Wizards...it depends.  Epic effect doesn't stack with beastlord mana regen, so most use Force Shield if that is available.  Cast time on wizard epic is also kind of annoying. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=152456" target="top"> Zatul </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
